            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion has softened, add your <strong>lean beef mince</strong> to the pan and cook over a high heat for 4-5 min or until browned all over, breaking it up with a wooden spoon as you go</p><p>While the lean beef mince is browning, add 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [2 tsp] </span><strong>black pepper</strong> to the pan (freshly ground is best!)</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1599748949089-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1599748949089-x400.jpg",
