        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Chinese-style</strong> <strong>lean</strong> <strong>beef & green pepper stir-fry</strong> over the <strong>cooked rice</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>chilli rounds </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and a generous grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
